title: Dalilah Muhammad talks 400m hurdles world record, doubt, and Kobe Bryant
description: Dalilah Muhammad of the USA is the reigning Olympic and world champion in the 400m hurdles. She opens up about the doubts she felt as a young runner, the inspiration she takes from late basketball star Kobe Bryant, and her targets for the Olympic year.
